{"type": "article", "id": 8911, "title": "模块化头戴式耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-27T07:16:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235256WTPDfv34wqNZjL8b.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Kilo 最近为丹麦耳机品牌 Aiaiai 设计了一款模块化的头戴式耳机。这款耳机内含多种不同的模块，包括外部轮廓，内部耳塞，通话器等都可以拆卸，最多有 360 种组成，可以满足不同环境下的音质需求。目前产品售价 140 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.aiaiai.dk/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235253mCgBFPrDGc7MbdfO.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235254ewlA4kG1MsWdJZz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352545910LNxEDtybg2ej.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235254mf49GiltKeQHzCyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235255zaj2sMfb7RFHgxGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235255qxP0iru2O71lypmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}